<a id="dingsx36570" href="javascript:dingsx('36570','http://so.gushiwen.org/shiwenv.aspx?id=155c8afc446f')">有用(7)</a><a id="paisx36570" style=" margin-left:10px;" href="javascript:paisx('36570','http://so.gushiwen.org/shiwenv.aspx?id=155c8afc446f')">没用(0)</a>
